BATES MOTEL ( SEASON 5 )
The fifth and final season of Bates Motel premiered on February 20 , 2017 , and concluded on April 24 , 2017 .
The season consisted of 10 episodes and aired on Mondays at 10 p.m. ET / PT on A&E.
The series itself is described as a " contemporary prequel " to the 1960 film Psycho , following the life of Norman Bates and his mother Norma prior to the events portrayed in the Hitchcock film .
However , the final season of the series loosely adapts the plot of Psycho .
The series takes place in the fictional town of White Pine Bay , Oregon .
The season was released on Blu - ray and DVD on September 19 , 2017 .
